"{\"uid\": \"balkaninsight.com-2024-08-06-gloves-off-woman-boxers-olympics-defeat-reignites-bulgarias-gender-battles-bi\", \"noun_phrases\": [{\"sentence\": \"Controversy over an old source of discord has erupted again in Bulgaria after Lin Yu-ting of Taiwan defeated Bulgarian woman boxer Svetlana Kamenova Staneva at the Olympics featherweight quarter-final in Paris at the weekend.\", \"from\": 0, \"to\": 225, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 63, \"end\": 71, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Bulgaria\", \"score\": 0.9999999999995453, \"rank\": 2.80973278562718e-13, \"text\": \"Bulgaria\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Bulgaria\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Bulgaria\"}, {\"begin\": 78, \"end\": 89, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Lin_Yu-ting\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Lin Yu-ting\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Lin_Yu-ting\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Lin_Yu-ting\"}, {\"begin\": 93, \"end\": 99, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Taiwan\", \"score\": 0.9999957400159262, \"rank\": 4.257659514699718e-06, \"text\": \"Taiwan\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Taiwan\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Taiwan\"}, {\"begin\": 109, \"end\": 118, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Bulgaria\", \"score\": 0.9993505301854616, \"rank\": 0.0006498905972654013, \"text\": \"Bulgarian\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Bulgaria\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Bulgaria\"}, {\"begin\": 204, \"end\": 209, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 0.9999999789733922, \"rank\": 2.1026546925940318e-08, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Controversy\", \"from\": 0, \"to\": 11}, {\"ngram\": \"an old source\", \"from\": 17, \"to\": 30}, {\"ngram\": \"discord\", \"from\": 34, \"to\": 41}, {\"ngram\": \"the Olympics\", \"from\": 160, \"to\": 172}, {\"ngram\": \"the weekend\", \"from\": 213, \"to\": 224}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Media commentators and politicians have spread ill-informed stereotypes and encouraged discriminatory rhetoric, according to media experts.\", \"from\": 227, \"to\": 366, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Media commentators\", \"from\": 227, \"to\": 245}, {\"ngram\": \"politicians\", \"from\": 250, \"to\": 261}, {\"ngram\": \"ill-informed stereotypes\", \"from\": 274, \"to\": 298}, {\"ngram\": \"discriminatory rhetoric\", \"from\": 314, \"to\": 337}, {\"ngram\": \"media experts\", \"from\": 352, \"to\": 365}]}, {\"sentence\": \"There had already been controversy internationally over the inclusion in the Paris Olympics of Lin Yu-ting and Imane Khelif of Algeria, who had previously been disqualified by another sporting body, the International Boxing Association, from 2023's boxing World Championships for failing gender eligibility tests.\", \"from\": 368, \"to\": 681, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 463, \"end\": 474, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Lin_Yu-ting\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Lin Yu-ting\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Lin_Yu-ting\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Lin_Yu-ting\"}, {\"begin\": 479, \"end\": 491, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Imane_Khelif\", \"score\": 0.9999996421621021, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Imane Khelif\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Imane_Khelif\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Imane_Khelif\"}, {\"begin\": 495, \"end\": 502, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Algeria\", \"score\": 0.9998446896331221, \"rank\": 0.00015533442000572787, \"text\": \"Algeria\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Algeria\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Algeria\"}, {\"begin\": 571, \"end\": 603, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Women's_International_Boxing_Association\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 1.0781080390508516e-29, \"text\": \"International Boxing Association\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Women's_International_Boxing_Association\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Women's_International_Boxing_Association\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"controversy\", \"from\": 391, \"to\": 402}, {\"ngram\": \"the inclusion\", \"from\": 424, \"to\": 437}, {\"ngram\": \"the Paris Olympics\", \"from\": 441, \"to\": 459}, {\"ngram\": \"another sporting body\", \"from\": 544, \"to\": 565}, {\"ngram\": \"World Championships\", \"from\": 624, \"to\": 643}, {\"ngram\": \"gender eligibility tests\", \"from\": 656, \"to\": 680}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The International Olympic Committee, however,questioned the reliability of these tests.\", \"from\": 683, \"to\": 770, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 687, \"end\": 718, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/International_Olympic_Committee\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"International Olympic Committee\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/International_Olympic_Committee\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/International_Olympic_Committee\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the reliability\", \"from\": 739, \"to\": 754}, {\"ngram\": \"these tests\", \"from\": 758, \"to\": 769}]}, {\"sentence\": \"During Sunday's bout, Kamenova raised the gender question openly by forming the letter \\\"X\\\" with her hands, symbolising female XX chromosomes, while her coach, Borislav Georgiev, held up a banner with the slogan: \\\"Save Woman Sports\\\" (sic).\", \"from\": 772, \"to\": 1010, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 898, \"end\": 900, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/XY_sex-determination_system\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 4.497751985277606e-19, \"text\": \"XX\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/XY_sex-determination_system\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/XY_sex-determination_system\"}, {\"begin\": 931, \"end\": 948, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Borislav_Georgiev\", \"score\": 0.9999998553007676, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Borislav Georgiev\", \"types\": [\"Q937857\", \"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Borislav_Georgiev\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Borislav_Georgiev\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Sunday's bout\", \"from\": 779, \"to\": 792}, {\"ngram\": \"Kamenova\", \"from\": 794, \"to\": 802}, {\"ngram\": \"the gender question\", \"from\": 810, \"to\": 829}, {\"ngram\": \"the letter \\\"X\", \"from\": 848, \"to\": 861}, {\"ngram\": \"her hands\", \"from\": 868, \"to\": 877}, {\"ngram\": \"her coach\", \"from\": 920, \"to\": 929}, {\"ngram\": \"a banner\", \"from\": 958, \"to\": 966}, {\"ngram\": \"the slogan\", \"from\": 972, \"to\": 982}, {\"ngram\": \"Save Woman Sports\", \"from\": 985, \"to\": 1002}, {\"ngram\": \"(sic\", \"from\": 1004, \"to\": 1008}]}, {\"sentence\": \"He later claimed that the Bulgarian fighter \\\"was robbed\\\" and referred disparagingly to Lin Yu-ting as \\\"a creature\\\".\", \"from\": 1011, \"to\": 1126, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1037, \"end\": 1046, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Bulgaria\", \"score\": 0.9993505301854616, \"rank\": 0.0006498905972654013, \"text\": \"Bulgarian\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Bulgaria\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Bulgaria\"}, {\"begin\": 1098, \"end\": 1109, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Lin_Yu-ting\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Lin Yu-ting\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Lin_Yu-ting\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Lin_Yu-ting\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"\\\"a creature\", \"from\": 1113, \"to\": 1124}]}, {\"sentence\": \"After the fight, Bulgarian President President Rumen Radev joined the fray, saying that Kamenova Staneva \\\"found bravery in fighting not only for victory in what people considered a lost game but also standing up for normalcy\\\".\", \"from\": 1128, \"to\": 1354, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1145, \"end\": 1164, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/President_of_Bulgaria\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Bulgarian President\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/President_of_Bulgaria\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/President_of_Bulgaria\"}, {\"begin\": 1175, \"end\": 1186, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Rumen_Radev\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Rumen Radev\", \"types\": [\"Q82955\", \"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Rumen_Radev\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Rumen_Radev\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the fight\", \"from\": 1134, \"to\": 1143}, {\"ngram\": \"the fray\", \"from\": 1194, \"to\": 1202}, {\"ngram\": \"Kamenova Staneva\", \"from\": 1216, \"to\": 1232}, {\"ngram\": \"bravery\", \"from\": 1240, \"to\": 1247}, {\"ngram\": \"victory\", \"from\": 1273, \"to\": 1280}, {\"ngram\": \"people\", \"from\": 1289, \"to\": 1295}, {\"ngram\": \"a lost game\", \"from\": 1307, \"to\": 1318}, {\"ngram\": \"normalcy\", \"from\": 1344, \"to\": 1352}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The Bulgarian Olympic Committee criticised the decision to allow Yu-ting and Khelif to participate at the tournament.\", \"from\": 1356, \"to\": 1473, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1360, \"end\": 1387, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Bulgarian_Olympic_Committee\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Bulgarian Olympic Committee\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Bulgarian_Olympic_Committee\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Bulgarian_Olympic_Committee\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the decision\", \"from\": 1399, \"to\": 1411}, {\"ngram\": \"Yu-ting\", \"from\": 1421, \"to\": 1428}, {\"ngram\": \"Khelif\", \"from\": 1433, \"to\": 1439}, {\"ngram\": \"the tournament\", \"from\": 1458, \"to\": 1472}]}, {\"sentence\": \"News media and major TV channels - including some credible outlets - also piled in, referring to Yu-ting and Khelif as \\\"transsexuals\\\" and as \\\"intersex\\\" persons, even though they were born female.\", \"from\": 1475, \"to\": 1670, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"News media\", \"from\": 1475, \"to\": 1485}, {\"ngram\": \"major TV channels\", \"from\": 1490, \"to\": 1507}, {\"ngram\": \"some credible outlets\", \"from\": 1520, \"to\": 1541}, {\"ngram\": \"Yu-ting\", \"from\": 1572, \"to\": 1579}, {\"ngram\": \"Khelif\", \"from\": 1584, \"to\": 1590}, {\"ngram\": \"\\\"transsexuals\", \"from\": 1594, \"to\": 1607}, {\"ngram\": \"\\\"intersex\\\" persons\", \"from\": 1616, \"to\": 1634}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The controversy even briefly overshadowedBulgaria's long-running governance crisisand the difficulties in combatting wildfires across the country.\", \"from\": 1671, \"to\": 1817, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"The controversy\", \"from\": 1671, \"to\": 1686}, {\"ngram\": \"even briefly overshadowedBulgaria's long-running governance\", \"from\": 1687, \"to\": 1746}, {\"ngram\": \"the difficulties\", \"from\": 1757, \"to\": 1773}, {\"ngram\": \"wildfires\", \"from\": 1788, \"to\": 1797}, {\"ngram\": \"the country\", \"from\": 1805, \"to\": 1816}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Many local media outlets cited a statement supportive of Kamenova issued by a Bulgarian organisation reportedly calling itself the Network for Protecting Women's Rights.\", \"from\": 1819, \"to\": 1988, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1897, \"end\": 1906, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Bulgaria\", \"score\": 0.9993505301854616, \"rank\": 0.0006498905972654013, \"text\": \"Bulgarian\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Bulgaria\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Bulgaria\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Many local media outlets\", \"from\": 1819, \"to\": 1843}, {\"ngram\": \"a statement\", \"from\": 1850, \"to\": 1861}, {\"ngram\": \"Kamenova\", \"from\": 1876, \"to\": 1884}, {\"ngram\": \"the Network\", \"from\": 1946, \"to\": 1957}, {\"ngram\": \"Women's Rights\", \"from\": 1973, \"to\": 1987}]}, {\"sentence\": \"However, no source for the statement could be traced and the organisation has no online presence.\", \"from\": 1990, \"to\": 2087, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"no source\", \"from\": 1999, \"to\": 2008}, {\"ngram\": \"the statement\", \"from\": 2013, \"to\": 2026}, {\"ngram\": \"the organisation\", \"from\": 2047, \"to\": 2063}, {\"ngram\": \"no online presence\", \"from\": 2068, \"to\": 2086}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The coverage of the dispute prompted the Association for European Journalists - Bulgaria to accuse the country's media of \\\"negligent\\\" behaviour.\", \"from\": 2089, \"to\": 2233, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"The coverage\", \"from\": 2089, \"to\": 2101}, {\"ngram\": \"the dispute\", \"from\": 2105, \"to\": 2116}, {\"ngram\": \"the Association\", \"from\": 2126, \"to\": 2141}, {\"ngram\": \"European Journalists - Bulgaria\", \"from\": 2146, \"to\": 2177}, {\"ngram\": \"the country's media\", \"from\": 2188, \"to\": 2207}, {\"ngram\": \"\\\"negligent\\\" behaviour\", \"from\": 2211, \"to\": 2232}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"Under-researched and stereotypical coverage of such topics not only fuels homophobia and misogyny; it may serve external interests to destabilise democracy but could also have a severe impact on the mental state of various groups and individuals.\", \"from\": 2235, \"to\": 2482, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"such topics\", \"from\": 2283, \"to\": 2294}, {\"ngram\": \"external interests\", \"from\": 2348, \"to\": 2366}, {\"ngram\": \"democracy\", \"from\": 2382, \"to\": 2391}, {\"ngram\": \"a severe impact\", \"from\": 2412, \"to\": 2427}, {\"ngram\": \"the mental state\", \"from\": 2431, \"to\": 2447}, {\"ngram\": \"various groups\", \"from\": 2451, \"to\": 2465}, {\"ngram\": \"individuals\", \"from\": 2470, \"to\": 2481}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Unfortunately, even respectable outlets were repeatedly negligent in covering the matter,\\\" it said in a statement.\", \"from\": 2483, \"to\": 2597, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"even respectable outlets\", \"from\": 2498, \"to\": 2522}, {\"ngram\": \"the matter\", \"from\": 2561, \"to\": 2571}, {\"ngram\": \"a statement\", \"from\": 2585, \"to\": 2596}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The bout in Paris has only highlighted deeper problems with gender issues in Bulgaria, journalist Peter Georgiev of sports podcast Victoria told BIRN.\", \"from\": 2599, \"to\": 2749, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2611, \"end\": 2616, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 0.9999999789733922, \"rank\": 2.1026546925940318e-08, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}, {\"begin\": 2676, \"end\": 2684, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Bulgaria\", \"score\": 0.9999999999995453, \"rank\": 2.80973278562718e-13, \"text\": \"Bulgaria\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Bulgaria\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Bulgaria\"}, {\"begin\": 2730, \"end\": 2738, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Queen_Victoria\", \"score\": 0.9999992172682476, \"rank\": 7.566100524734345e-07, \"text\": \"Victoria\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Queen_Victoria\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Queen_Victoria\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"The bout\", \"from\": 2599, \"to\": 2607}, {\"ngram\": \"deeper problems\", \"from\": 2638, \"to\": 2653}, {\"ngram\": \"gender issues\", \"from\": 2659, \"to\": 2672}, {\"ngram\": \"sports podcast\", \"from\": 2715, \"to\": 2729}, {\"ngram\": \"BIRN\", \"from\": 2744, \"to\": 2748}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"For years, Bulgarian society has been extremely sensitive to sex and gender issues, but opinions are often ill-informed.\", \"from\": 2751, \"to\": 2872, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2763, \"end\": 2772, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Bulgaria\", \"score\": 0.9993505301854616, \"rank\": 0.0006498905972654013, \"text\": \"Bulgarian\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Bulgaria\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Bulgaria\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"years\", \"from\": 2756, \"to\": 2761}, {\"ngram\": \"sex and gender issues\", \"from\": 2813, \"to\": 2834}, {\"ngram\": \"opinions\", \"from\": 2840, \"to\": 2848}]}, {\"sentence\": \"In the case of Khelif and Yu-ting, a number of coaches, politicians and even professional sports commentators reacted emotionally to Kamenova's loss, showing little understanding of terms such as transgender and intersex,\\\" Georgiev told BIRN.\", \"from\": 2873, \"to\": 3115, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the case\", \"from\": 2876, \"to\": 2884}, {\"ngram\": \"Khelif\", \"from\": 2888, \"to\": 2894}, {\"ngram\": \"Yu-ting\", \"from\": 2899, \"to\": 2906}, {\"ngram\": \"a number\", \"from\": 2908, \"to\": 2916}, {\"ngram\": \"coaches\", \"from\": 2920, \"to\": 2927}, {\"ngram\": \"politicians\", \"from\": 2929, \"to\": 2940}, {\"ngram\": \"even professional sports commentators\", \"from\": 2945, \"to\": 2982}, {\"ngram\": \"Kamenova's loss\", \"from\": 3006, \"to\": 3021}, {\"ngram\": \"little understanding\", \"from\": 3031, \"to\": 3051}, {\"ngram\": \"terms\", \"from\": 3055, \"to\": 3060}, {\"ngram\": \"transgender\", \"from\": 3069, \"to\": 3080}, {\"ngram\": \"intersex\", \"from\": 3085, \"to\": 3093}, {\"ngram\": \"Georgiev\", \"from\": 3096, \"to\": 3104}, {\"ngram\": \"BIRN\", \"from\": 3110, \"to\": 3114}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"Their complete disregard for the facts and public outrage amplified misinformation and fuelled a wave of unjustified hatred,\\\" he added.\", \"from\": 3117, \"to\": 3253, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Their complete disregard\", \"from\": 3118, \"to\": 3142}, {\"ngram\": \"the facts\", \"from\": 3147, \"to\": 3156}, {\"ngram\": \"public outrage\", \"from\": 3161, \"to\": 3175}, {\"ngram\": \"misinformation\", \"from\": 3186, \"to\": 3200}, {\"ngram\": \"a wave\", \"from\": 3213, \"to\": 3219}, {\"ngram\": \"unjustified hatred\", \"from\": 3223, \"to\": 3241}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Georgiev sees the case as representative of a wider failure by the media and society to properly tackle gender issues: \\\"This is especially disappointing because it shifts the attention away from the very real debate about fairness in sports,\\\" he said.\", \"from\": 3255, \"to\": 3506, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Georgiev\", \"from\": 3255, \"to\": 3263}, {\"ngram\": \"the case\", \"from\": 3269, \"to\": 3277}, {\"ngram\": \"representative\", \"from\": 3281, \"to\": 3295}, {\"ngram\": \"a wider failure\", \"from\": 3299, \"to\": 3314}, {\"ngram\": \"the media\", \"from\": 3318, \"to\": 3327}, {\"ngram\": \"society\", \"from\": 3332, \"to\": 3339}, {\"ngram\": \"gender issues\", \"from\": 3359, \"to\": 3372}, {\"ngram\": \"the attention\", \"from\": 3426, \"to\": 3439}, {\"ngram\": \"the very real debate\", \"from\": 3450, \"to\": 3470}, {\"ngram\": \"fairness\", \"from\": 3477, \"to\": 3485}, {\"ngram\": \"sports\", \"from\": 3489, \"to\": 3495}]}, {\"sentence\": \"He noted that the dispute between the International Olympic Committee and the International Boxing Association also caused problems for the bo